@startuml activity_manage_site_information
title Activity Diagram - ManageSiteInformation

start
:Overseas Import Site opens profile management;
:Select site profile to update;
fork
  :Update Site profile name/info;
fork again
  :Update delivery times (ship and air);
fork again
  :Update merchandise catalog;
end fork
:Submit changes;
if (Delivery times are positive integers?) then (yes)
  :System saves changes in Site Information;
  :System notifies International Ordering Department of changes;
  stop
else (no)
  :Display Validation Error (invalid times);
  :Prompt to re-enter delivery times;
  stop
endif
@enduml
